# v1.32.11 hotfix-sweep marker (transient — created by --quick mode,
# cleared by a successful non-quick run). Must be gitignored so its
# presence doesn't trip release.sh's clean-working-tree check before
# the script can detect the marker and refuse to release.
.hotfix-sweep-quick
